articles.description: Amanze Egekeze poured in 28 points, including a go-ahead 3-pointer with 60 seconds left in the game, to propel Belmont to a 75-70 victory over Tennessee Tech on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Egekeze lifts Belmont to 75-70 win over Tennessee Tech

articles.description: Colorado State suspended interim head coach Steve Barnes just hours before Saturday's Mountain West game and assistant coach Jase Herl took his place, helping the team snap a seven-game losing streak with a 90-79 win over San Jose State.
articles.headline: Interim coach Steve Barnes suspended before game; assistant Jase Herl guides Rams to victory

articles.description: Chris Cokley had 15 points and nine rebounds and UAB rallied from nine down with less than four minutes to go for a 61-56 win on Saturday night.
articles.headline: UAB rallies past Rice 61-56

articles.description: The Tigers take down the Bulldogs 78-61 to earn their first sweep since the 1985-86 season.
articles.headline: No. 8 Auburn sweeps UGA in regular season

images.caption: The Tigers take down the Bulldogs 78-61 to earn their first sweep since the 1985-86 season.
images.name: No. 8 Auburn sweeps UGA in regular season

articles.description: Shakur Juiston scored 22 points and grabbed 14 rebounds and UNLV beat Wyoming 85-70 on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Juiston leads UNLV past Wyoming 85-70

articles.description: Khalil Ahmad had 31 points and Kyle Allman added 21 and Cal State Fullerton made five free throws down the stretch to seal a 68-66 win over UC Davis on Saturday night.
articles.headline: Cal State Fullerton holds off UC Davis for 68-66 win

videos.description: With the shot clock about to expire, TCU's JD Miller nails the step-back 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Miller beats the buzzer with 3-ball

videos.description: Cody Martin finds Caleb Martin cutting to the rim for the layup and the and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Nevada executes inbound play for 3-point chance

videos.description: TCU's Kenrich Williams drives right down the lane for the easy layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Williams breezes right by Nevada for easy layup

videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson breaks out the crossover moves before driving and burying the contested layup.
videos.headline: Robinson drains tough layup

videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson tries driving down the paint but is denied by Lindsey Drew in the first half.
videos.headline: Nevada's Drew rejects Robinson

videos.description: TCU's Jaylen Fisher dishes it off to Vladimir Brodziansky in the post for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Fisher finds Brodziansky for layup

videos.description: Despite the contact from Nevada's Jordan Caroline, TCU's JD Miller sinks the 3-pointer for a chance at a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Miller drains long ball for 4-point chance

videos.description: Nevada's Cody Martin swings the ball to Jordan Caroline down low for the layup and the 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Caroline converts layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Nevada's Hallice Cooke finds Cody Martin rolling to the basket for the loud dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Martin throws down emphatic dunk

videos.description: After grabbing the defensive rebound, TCU's Alex Robinson splits defenders and takes it all the way for the layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Robinson goes coast-to-coast for layup

videos.description: Nevada's Caleb Martin tries going up for a layup in the paint but is blocked by Vladimir Brodziansky in the second half.
videos.headline: Brodziansky denies Martin's attempt

videos.description: TCU's Jaylen Fisher splits through the defense and sinks the tough layup for the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Fisher finishes coast-to-coast layup for and-1 chance
